graph LR
    RHODSOperator[RHODS Operator<br/>OpenDataHub Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    RHODSOperator -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    RHODSOperator -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+<br/>Routes, OAuth, Security]
    RHODSOperator -->|ingress| GatewayAPICRDs[Gateway API CRDs v1<br/>Gateway, GatewayClass, HTTPRoute]
    RHODSOperator -->|TLS certs| IngressOperator[OpenShift Ingress Operator<br/>Default ingress controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    RHODSOperator -.->|metrics| PrometheusOperator[Prometheus Operator v0.68+<br/>ServiceMonitor, PrometheusRule]
    RHODSOperator -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio / OpenShift Service Mesh 2.4+<br/>EnvoyFilter, DestinationRule]
    RHODSOperator -.->|custom certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.11+<br/>Optional certificate management]

    %% Internal ODH Components (Deployed by Operator)
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Jupyter lifecycle]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>ML pipeline orchestration]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| KServe[KServe<br/>Model serving platform]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Kuberay[Kuberay Operator<br/>Ray cluster management]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job queue & resource quota]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>Model explainability]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ML model metadata]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| TrainingOperator[Training Operator<br/>Distributed training]
    RHODSOperator -->|deploys| FeastOperator[Feast Operator<br/>Feature store]

    %% Gateway Infrastructure (Deployed by Operator)
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| GatewayClass[GatewayClass<br/>data-science-gateway-class]
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| Gateway[Gateway<br/>data-science-gateway<br/>openshift-ingress ns]
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| EnvoyFilter[EnvoyFilter<br/>authn-filter<br/>ext_authz]
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| KubeAuthProxy[kube-auth-proxy<br/>OAuth2/OIDC authentication]
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| OAuthClient[OAuthClient<br/>odh<br/>IntegratedOAuth mode]

    %% Authentication Providers
    KubeAuthProxy -->|authenticates| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>IntegratedOAuth mode]
    KubeAuthProxy -->|authenticates| OIDCProvider[External OIDC Provider<br/>ROSA/OIDC mode]

    %% Component Integration with Gateway
    NotebookController -->|creates| HTTPRoutes[HTTPRoute CRs<br/>per notebook workbench]
    Dashboard -->|creates| DashboardHTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>dashboard ingress]
    HTTPRoutes -->|references| Gateway
    DashboardHTTPRoute -->|references| Gateway

    %% Component RBAC Pattern
    NotebookController -->|injects| KubeRBACProxySidecars[kube-rbac-proxy sidecars<br/>per-workload auth]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| ServiceMonitors[ServiceMonitor CRs<br/>component metrics]
    RHODSOperator -->|creates| PrometheusRules[PrometheusRule CRs<br/>platform alerts]
    ServiceMonitors -->|scraped by| PrometheusStack[Prometheus - RHOAI monitoring]
    PrometheusStack -->|federates to| ClusterMonitoring[OpenShift Cluster Monitoring]

    %% External Services
    RHODSOperator -->|pulls images| Quay[quay.io]
    RHODSOperator -->|pulls images| RedHatRegistry[registry.redhat.io]
    KServe -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage]
    Pipelines -->|pipeline storage| S3

    %% Operator Management
    OLM[OLM - Operator Lifecycle Manager] -->|installs/updates| RHODSOperator

